      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_2F045AF0-22F6-0135-C91F-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Your message appears in the preview text of the conversation [1] and at the top of the individual thread [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
